Package com.straxov.entitiy

Interface EntityFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
Ð¡ityFactory
public interface EntityFactory
Factory interface for creating simulation entities (Banks, Workers, and Spenders). Provides creation methods for all major entity types in the economic simulation.
